summary: Adds a lore friendly cabin that included all the things you could ever want, by the lake running through winterhold
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/20386-1-1342129893.jpg[/img]

This house mod was intended to be a winter cottage near the lake off the road to winterhold,it is very lore freindly, and contains no mannuiqines and is used to stay and store you items.
The area is hand crafting around the lake and forms a magical place to stay and rest your feet.

 [youtube]mp3KoxMPQOM[/youtube]

 [youtube]9AohLm7FS-Y[/youtube]

 [youtube]M4YNPLwOc0c[/youtube]

[size=6]====Feature=====[/size]
[color=green]-Lore friendly extreme[/color]
[color=green]-All the basics[/color]
[color=green]-Alchemy table+enchanting table[/color]
[color=green]-Realistic frost embeded lighting outside and in with dynamic fog around lights[/color]
[color=green]-Blacksmithing and storage for your crafting needs[/color]
[color=green]-Chopping blocks galor[/color]
[color=green]-Training dummies outside[/color]
[color=green]-Great view seating area[/color]
[color=green]-Roads/paths and hills recreated to fit around the cottage[/color]
[color=green]-animated gates[/color]
[color=green]-Glacier wind sweeps for realism[/color]
[color=green]-Followers work perfectly in the area[/color]
[color=green]-And more[/color]



[size=6]====Changelog====[/size]
V1.0 Release

Patches coming soon for 4 limit lighing bug
